medal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations EJ.\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are still number one for all filipino.\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tsaka may next year pa naman.\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Di man ngayon pero may bukas pa. Keep fighting!\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 4019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fighting.\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, Filipinos are calling for more government support for the country's athletes.\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See how our athletes shine and create breakthroughs despite all the circumstances?\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"May the state invest more on these aspects of sports instead of doubting the athletes in this community.A salute to all our Filipino athletes, win or lose!\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mabuhay kayo!\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PONDOHAN NIYO NA UTANG NA LOOBhttps://t.co/yvAIKV5sPq  Salamat sa laban, EJ!- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4443, \"end\": 4450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salamat_(region)\", \"score\": 0.7911647727923034, \"rank\": 0.1403508771930023, \"text\": \"Salamat\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salamat_(region)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salamat_(region)\"}, {\"begin\": 4454, \"end\": 4459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.170857923150424e-14, \"text\": \"laban\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strained_yogurt\"}, {\"begin\": 4461, \"end\": 4463, \"title\": \"http: